    <blockquote>
      <p parentName="blockquote">{`Monad is a way of creating a functional-friendly data structure. "A monoid in the category of endofunctors." In laymen terms: a pattern for pairing data with a set of predictable behaviours that let it interact with other data + behaviour pairings (other monads).`}</p>
    </blockquote>
    <p>{`Why do I need a data structure for one value? It is a wrapper with a set of behaviours with it that allow it to be friendly to functional concepts.`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-javascript"
      }}>{`// a wrapper around a single value
